        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Yeah, I'm not a fan of using `nvim_echo` for log messages, although I don't care that much and could easily be persuaded otherwise. To me it feels like mixing two different things that shouldn't be combined. And while I can see the use of sending log messages to the message ui, I don't think it should be that tightly integrated (especially when I'd like to integrate it tighter with `:log` instead).",
